queries.sql: SELECT `movies`.*, `seasons`.`season`, `seasons`.`series_id`, `series`.`title` as `series_title`, `series`.`imdb_id` as `series_imdb_id`, `series`.`tmdb_id` as `series_tmdb_id`, `movies`.*, sum(visitors.views) as views FROM `movies` LEFT JOIN `seasons` ON `seasons`.`id` = `movies`.`season_id` LEFT JOIN `series` ON `series`.`id` = `seasons`.`series_id` LEFT JOIN `visitors` ON `visitors`.`movie_id` = `movies`.`id` WHERE `movies`.`type` = 'episode' AND `visitors`.`views` != 0 GROUP BY `movies`.`id`, `movies`.`id` ORDER BY `views` DESC LIMIT 10
